      "translation": "拉 嗒 嘀 嗒 嘀 嗒 嘀 嗒"
    },
    {
      "time": 67.4,
      "time_str": "01:07.400",
      "text": "There are many secrets that I'd like to share with you",
      "translation": "这有很多我想要跟你分享的秘密"
    },
    {
      "time": 71.62,
      "time_str": "01:11.620",
      "text": "I will show you magic if the words you say are true",
      "translation": "如果你说的都是真的 我就会为你表演魔术"
    },
    {
      "time": 75.18,
      "time_str": "01:15.180",
      "text": "Imagine that the wildest dreams are in this mystery",
